title: [Miasmal Forest, Old Road]
description: Small pearls of dew are gathered on the tall blades of grass growing in the middle of the old road.  Dead and dying trees line the road like ancient, stoic sentries.  A faint odor of putrefaction hovers in the fog.

The moisture gathered on the tall blades of grass growing in the middle of the old road glow like dull pearls in the weak sunlight.  Dead and dying trees line the road like ancient, stoic sentries.  A faint odor of putrefaction hovers in the fog.
